1. 创建 api.js 核心模块:
```javascript
const API_BASE = '/api/cses';

const ApiService = {
  // 默认请求头
  getHeaders() {
    return {
      'Content-Type': 'application/json',
      'appType': 'bct',
      'device': '',  // WEB 为空
      'language': 'zh',
      'deviceId': this.getDeviceId(),
      'appVersion': '1.0.120',
      'timeZone': 'Asia/Shanghai',
      'Authorization': `Bearer ${this.getToken()}`
    };
  },

  // 统一请求方法
  async request(endpoint, options = {}) {
    const url = `${API_BASE}${endpoint}`;
    const config = {
      headers: this.getHeaders(),
      ...options
    };

    try {
      const response = await fetch(url, config);
      const data = await response.json();

      if (data.status !== 'success') {
        throw new Error(data.message || '请求失败');
      }
      return data.data;
    } catch (error) {
      Toast.error(error.message);
      throw error;
    }
  }
};
```

2. 实现 Bot Agent API 接口封装:
- `BotAgentApi.create(config)` - POST /bot-agent/config
- `BotAgentApi.get(botUserId)` - GET /bot-agent/config/{botUserId}
- `BotAgentApi.delete(botUserId)` - DELETE /bot-agent/config/{botUserId}
- `BotAgentApi.listEnabled()` - GET /bot-agent/configs/enabled
- `BotAgentApi.regenerateToken(botUserId)` - POST /bot-agent/config/{botUserId}/regenerate-token

3. 实现 Token 管理:
- 从 localStorage 读取/存储 Token
- Token 过期处理和刷新机制
- 生成唯一 deviceId 并持久化

4. 实现全局 Toast 通知组件用于错误提示

